#. Tag: para
#: storage_multipath.xml:3801
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"\t More often than not, the manual activation will succeed and allow\t too "
"proceed with system boot (usually by simply logging out from the\t emergency "
"shell) and examine the situation further in the booted\t system.\t"
