#. Tag: para
#: storage_multipath.xml:3807
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"\t If manual activation fails, you will probably see error messages\t that "
"provide clues what is going wrong. You can also\t try the commands again "
"with increased verbosity.\t"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: storage_multipath.xml:3814
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"\t At this point, you should have some idea what went wrong (if not,\t "
"contact &suse; support and be prepared to answer most of the\t questions "
"raised above).\t"
